summary:
I am currently working as a freelance Community Manager on the game Stellaris on behalf of Paradox Interactive. During the 2 years in this role I have developed all sorts of skills in things such as influencer management, live content, events, social media management and more.

Before working with Paradox I was a full time content creator on Twitch and have 4 Years Experience running a Stream Team and Player Community for various Science Fiction and Strategy computer games which raised over Â£100,000 for various charitable causes.
